<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Web Application Error</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .container {
      width: 85%;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .icon {
      height: 50px;
      position: absolute;
      right: 30px;
      top: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }

    div {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    strong {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 90px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
      text-align: left;
    }

    pre {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="/image/nodejsDark.svg" alt="Node.js Error Icon" class="icon">
    <h1>Web Application Error</h1>
    <p>The application could not run because of the following error:</p>
    <h2>Details</h2>
    <% if (error.status) { %>
    <div><strong>Type Error:</strong> <%= error.status %></div>
    <% } %>
    <div><strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></div>
    <% if (error.path) { %>
    <div><strong>File:</strong> <%= error.path %></div>
    <% } %>
    <h2>Trace</h2>
    <pre><%= error.stack %></pre>
  </div>
</body>

</html>